WEBVTT

00:00.400 --> 00:02.870
We'd like to get a dog for the kids to play with.

00:03.165 --> 00:05.910
They've been pestering us about it for so long!

00:06.340 --> 00:07.975
Sounds like a great idea!

00:08.500 --> 00:10.375
What kind of breed are you looking for?

00:10.950 --> 00:13.595
A small breed would probably be best for us.

00:13.845 --> 00:16.115
You should get a Boston Terrier.

00:16.415 --> 00:19.055
We have two of them, they're awesome dogs!

00:19.650 --> 00:21.495
They have so much personality!

00:21.805 --> 00:23.455
They really love the kids.

00:24.055 --> 00:26.860
They look after us, and they are part of the family!

00:27.380 --> 00:28.920
Plus, they look gorgeous!

00:29.000 --> 00:30.700
They sound perfect!

